  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/712667498197155862/966307899309715476/drill_logo_copie.png?width=1440&amp;height=504\" alt=\"\" width=\"1123\" height=\"393\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;-</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjXvVIzBkFmmGjOBAq-zGIg/channels\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/891582128310063164/952947600833777724/youtube.png\" width=\"165\" height=\"90\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/k3fGJwJqzu\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/891582128310063164/952947601219665960/discord.png\" width=\"165\" height=\"90\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/unsusualsquad/\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/891582128310063164/953302370723463228/reddit.png\" width=\"164\" height=\"89\" /></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;-</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"> <strong>Unusual Drill adds new efficient tools to mine large area (3x3) (Drills, Saws and Spades). Each tool has 3 unique materials tiers, using prismarine, nether brick, and more depending on the tool !</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">(install&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jei\" rel=\"nofollow\">JEI</a>&nbsp;to see all the recipes)&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Tools base used in crafts&nbsp; :</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/712667498197155862/966307681755344946/emboutl_render.png\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Drills</strong></span>, <strong>Tier 1 :</strong>&nbsp;Iron, <strong>Tier&nbsp;2 :</strong>&nbsp;Heart of the Sea, <strong>Tier&nbsp;3 :</strong>&nbsp;Netherite</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/712667498197155862/966307681495306240/drill_render.png\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Saw</span>, Tier 1 :</strong>&nbsp;Gold, <strong>Tier 2 :</strong>&nbsp;Nether Bricks, <strong>Tier 3 :</strong>&nbsp;Diamond</span><br /><br /><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/712667498197155862/966307682040545281/saw_render.png\" /></p>\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spade</span>, Tier 1 :</strong>&nbsp;Bamboo, <strong>Tier 2 :</strong>&nbsp;Blaze Rod, <strong>Tier 3 :</strong>&nbsp;End Rod</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/712667498197155862/966307682317385778/spade_render.png\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>multidrill</strong> </span>: <strong>tier 1</strong> : ghast tear,<strong> tier 2 :</strong> totem of undying, <strong>tier 3 :</strong> nether star<br /></span></p>\n<p><strong>the multidrill mine all type of blocks !</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/922393407802986496/973235819211005982/multidrill_render.png\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>You can put Unusual Drill in your modpack !<br /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
